window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Amir </b>is a man who knows what he wants... but it's not the woman who is pressuring him for marriage. As he struggles with ending a relationship that's run its course, fate throws him a curveball named <b>Koryn</b>.</p> <p>Fresh from a devastating betrayal, Koryn thought she'd found her happily-ever-after when her fiancé swept her away on a romantic month-long vacation. Instead, his shocking ultimatum forces her to choose between love and her core values. She flees, convinced romance isn't in the cards for her.</p> <p>When Amir and Koryn's paths unexpectedly cross, their connection is instant and electric. But with both nursing fresh wounds, is this real love or just a rebound? They say the heart's greatest rewards come with the biggest risks — but are they ready to gamble everything on a second chance at happiness?</p>"; 
